      • getWithJAASKey

        public static Group getWithJAASKey(JAASSystem _jaasSystem,
                   String _jaasKey)
                            throws EFapsException
        Returns for given parameter _jaasKey the instance of class Group. The parameter _jaasKey is the name of the group used in the given JAAS system for the group.
        Parameters:
        _jaasSystem - JAAS system for which the JAAS key is named
        _jaasKey - key in the foreign JAAS system for which the group is searched
        Returns:
        instance of class Group, or null if group is not found
        Throws:
        EFapsException - if group with JAAS key could not be fetched from eFaps
        See Also:
        get(long)
